&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and analytical skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Empathy and a passion for delivering excellent service to customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Driven, self-motivated, collaborative and highly flexible team player approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-learner, and an avid problem-solver&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to effectively prioritize and execute tasks in a high-pressure environment&lt;/li&gt;
